These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  dancer, engineer, firefighter, entrepreneur, writer, nurse
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking, writing
1. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the dancer is on the left of the firefighter##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the writer is on the right of the engineer##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Job   | nurse | dancer  | firefighter    | entrepreneur  | engineer      | writer    |
| Hobby      | puzzles  | writing | woodworking | gardening | skydiving | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, basketball, surfing, skateboarding, rowing
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
9. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Sport   | handball   | skateboarding | water-polo | rowing | surfing     | basketball  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, tram, skateboard, motorbike, roller
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, colombian, german, polish
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the german##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the polish##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the british##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the chinese is the person driving the skateboard##1
9. the person driving the tram is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Transport   | skateboard   | roller   | motorbike      | bus | snowmobile  | tram   |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | argentine | british   | german | colombian |

