.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: ship, train, airplane, car, motorbike, van
There are 6 different nationalities: american, australian, brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
1. the mexican is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the american##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the australian is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
5. the german is the person driving the van##1
6. the person driving the train is on the right of the brazilian##1
7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
9. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Transport   | van    | airplane    | ship | motorbike     | train   | car     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

