3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person traveling to venice is the person driving the trike##1
6. the person traveling to prague is the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
