.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: singing, fishing, puzzles, filmmaking, dancing, sudoku
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Hobby   | sudoku | singing  | dancing     | puzzles    | fishing  | filmmaking          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

