.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: swimming, snowboarding, sailing, handball, water-polo, tennis
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person who's sport is swimming##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Sport   | snowboarding   | swimming | tennis | water-polo | sailing | handball |

