4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up     | juice | almond-milk | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Hobby        | skydiving | cooking | video-games | rock-climbing   | photography    | dancing |

