.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-14::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: brown, ebony, orange, lilac, light-blue, black
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: folk, funk, indie, jazz, metal, reggae
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of indie is the person who likes black##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the left of the fan of indie##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person who likes brown is on the right of the fan of funk##1
8. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
9. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |    4    |      5       |     6     |
| Color         | ebony | light-blue | brown | lilac | orange | black |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | funk      | jazz    | folk    | metal        | indie     |

