.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-17::.
6 different pets are kept: cat, goat, hamster, rat, snake, turtle
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, november, october, april, august, july
1. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the rat is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |    5    |       6       |
| Pet     | snake  | rat       | turtle   | cat      | hamster | goat          |
| Birthday   | august | june | october | november | april | july |

