6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
